name: balanced vacation
description:
After 2 years of being hit by the covid-19 pandemic, and we are staying at home to stop the spread of the virus, we need a balance in life, which is to go on vacation.

 Holidays make our bodies recharge and refresh. I think this is the right time, at the end of 2021. And after so many million people are vaccinated to be safe.

 I took this photo when I was on vacation to a small uninhabited island, the water is clean and without any plastic waste.
